OL,3,CDrug driver 'nearly 10 times' over
OL,4,Climit admits causing motorcyclist's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA driver who was "nearly ten times"
OL,8,Fover the drug drive limit has admitted
OL,9,Fto causing the death of a motorcyclist.
OL,11,FCormac Sale pleaded guilty to causing
OL,12,Fthe death of Spencer Rothwell-Poole,
OL,13,F22, in a crash on Chorley Road in
OL,14,FBolton.
OL,16,FPolice said a Skoda Fabia car "crossed
OL,17,Fdirectly into the path of an oncoming
OL,18,Fmotorbike" on 14 December 2024.
OL,19,FMotorcyclist, Spencer, died at the
OL,20,Fscene.
