OL,7,FSale appeared at Bolton Crown Court on
OL,8,FFriday, 30 January, where he pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to causing death by dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FDave Bruce, prosecuting, said the
OL,13,Fdefendant "was nearly 10 times over
OL,14,Fthe legal limit", telling the court
OL,15,Fthat the part of the Crown's case
OL,16,Fwould relate to 'the drugs taken at
OL,17,Fthe time'.
