OL,7,FSale had attended court on bail, and
OL,8,FMr James had asked the judge to allow
OL,9,Fhim to be bailed again to 'put in
OL,10,Forder everything in his life'.
OL,12,FMr James said: "He is well aware of
OL,13,Fthe sentence that is going to follow,
OL,14,Fit is inevitable", but Sale was
OL,15,Fremanded into custody in Bolton ahead
OL,16,Fof sentencing.
OL,18,FSpencer's father Rick previously paid
OL,19,Ftribute to his son, describing him as
OL,20,Fhis 'baby boy'.
