OL,4,Climit admits causing motorcyclist's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe said: "My son had autism and found
OL,8,Fit difficult to go out and speak to
OL,9,Fpeople. But when he put that helmet on
OL,10,Fhe was a different person and loved
OL,11,Fthe open road.
OL,13,F"He wasn't just a son and a brother,
OL,14,Fhe was our best friend and loved
OL,15,Feveryone. My heart is shattered but I
OL,16,Fhad to do this as we've had so many
OL,17,Fbeautiful words.
OL,19,F"Until I see you again my sweet boy
OL,20,Flook after mum and come to me and Josh
OL,21,Fin our dreams."
